</taxonomicNameLabel>
is only known from a single locality in central SW 
<collectingCountry box="[1057,1124,1774,1799]" name="China" pageId="6" pageNumber="107">China</collectingCountry>
(middle-high altitude areas of the NW Sichuan Province).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,2015]" box="[199,579,1846,1871]" pageId="6" pageNumber="107">
